 go looking for the owners. Try it with 18 level 60 mages and 18 mage pets and full afterburners, go looking for your rezzes before you leave.  18 wizzies might do some damage before they evac out, better hope there's no adds (36,000 hp is not likely a dead level 65 dragon).  About the only hope there is bind, nuke, evac, gate, and repeat (ok they might do it) Try it with 15 level 60 warriors and three level 60 clerics and you have a better than average chance of repeatedly killing dragons all day and having fun!  (Don't even think about adding those badly needed healers to the caster raids, there won't be time to get a light heal on the pet before it's toast)
